data.text:
From Yakima playing for the Yakima Valley College Yaks to playing pro basketball for the Milwaukee Bucks, Marjon Beauchamp is home in Yakima to do an autograph signing for any and all.

July 19 at 6 p.m. at YVC

It was just last year he was playing for the Yaks in Yakima. So proud to see him where he is now.

And he keeps it humble all the way through.

Show some love for Marjon Beauchamp by attending his autograph signing on Tuesday, July 19 at Yakima Valley College gym starting at 6 p.m. More details on the MJB Facebook page.
